A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Public Safety – Police Accountability – Deadline for Completion of Investigation
3 FOR the purpose of requiring the investigating unit of a law enforcement agency to
4 complete its review of a certain complaint and forward its investigatory files to the
5 administrative charging committee within a certain period of time after the filing of
6 the complaint; and generally relating to police accountability.
