1 of this subtitle;
2 (4) review any body camera footage that may be relevant to the matters
3 covered in the complaint of misconduct;
4 (5) authorize a police officer called to appear before an administrative
5 charging committee to be accompanied by a representative;
6 (6) issue a written opinion that describes in detail its findings,
